{"h5304b562g5bcag405fga823gee6bf28d8d78": ["Go! Bite! <i>Bite</i>!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "6e468230-bafc-bdc4-a7a0-0fbebbf798f7"], "h6ff13678gb2e2g4084g94e0gfb0f84fddae3": ["Go home. Cave. Mother!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "dab239b8-025b-cf46-1745-d2ebf8cb9d9a"], "hed469209g21bdg4dddgae73g30e1f437fdc0": ["I have a camp. You're welcome there.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "edd6032f-cca5-df56-4acd-dcf09f49041c"], "hde1c1d2dg3463g4a82gb942g67e11adbe0a9": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "0192183d-d5f7-befe-5a6b-3da3ff82ae04"], "h0a97bd90g1c01g405dg95e7gcd5b0c8ea8de": ["Mother gone. Hungry!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "96e34773-2b73-3ae5-7b2b-1bbb134cb249"], "h9656d835g86d3g4e7egb544g436a113cb4cf": ["Run! Get me!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "86b0e5af-271c-edfe-4b6b-7b0d51a03f25"], "hf0389c6dg0e34g4ae4g851dge47ff117bc3a": ["Hurt me! Run! Where?", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "dab0c6d9-f5d1-16f0-ed7d-165cea3948e7"], "h1a318daag6544g4999gaacdg0cc849ffdb3d": ["See those posts? Run toward them.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "0d49aca3-c896-c559-38f0-b71746bfc057"], "h9e460c92g5a1fg42bdg8b7cgf1e00bf03133": ["Safe. There? Run!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "fc863274-0cfa-866f-f74d-4dd6723f28c5"], "ha1e874ebg10f3g4e34gbb4cg9ab8ea350346": ["No! Hurt! Run!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "6ba808c2-ce68-1838-0c5e-3915d9681233"], "h7f27d155g54c8g4a19gabf7g178b2647b12d": ["The goblins are responsible for your pain. Kill them.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "c05e06f7-7447-5d1e-c3b9-0f8c4b9fe03c"], "hb7ce7b45g381fg46f7gb4e1g8f83e5027edd": ["Bite. Eat! Bite!", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "c38b866b-47c2-327e-ae14-02e49cd19bca"], "hd2cb832dg8b99g4ff1g86d8g9ec043987832": ["The goblins hurt you. They deserve your fury.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "2d1a8ad2-91fc-2ac2-3ffd-8ab66dbfa0d7"], "hf4825920gbab1g40f5ga473g05856c074551": ["They won't hurt you if you run to those posts.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "8ebdb7f2-93a2-bbb3-48b6-e228d47b8664"], "h28e28b66gb7fbg41c3gb938g70f72a28a764": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "8e9bc462-ba39-71e0-9d5a-ab1a5e2e4c47"], "hcdf72064g7233g447cg85bbg696266eb9138": ["*Talons tensed to strike, beak aching to rend - the cub wants you gone.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "76e6e917-50e9-1c54-ac32-79d176f4296c"], "h273a203bg97b1g4f50g9934g157887705590": ["*Squawk!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "aab4a4fb-55b1-3342-f956-2afb0b10a828"], "hcf12d41bgef1bg45efg8b12g04e5fc35a8b9": ["*The cub looks at you with dulled eyes. He longs for home.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "55395fef-5ce7-0228-0012-e0efb77aadde"], "h85f8dc0dgc166g42bfg8d93ge0e48f34a4e4": ["*Hoo!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "6fda0ccc-c0ca-249d-9a67-ebd4f335840c"], "hb4585124g4731g4515gac6agd55eccf07b1e": ["<i>Beckon him closer.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "a7f0f83a-bae6-e867-187c-d87d8f6ec264"], "hae820bafg45e6g497fg8adfg17ad8a6900ff": ["<i>Kneel down - you won't hurt him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "7faad52a-370d-3e64-1f0f-613266942e1e"], "h23241cb4g6cb5g47ddg80bega4bdea0198a8": ["*You notice a shiver run through his feathered coat - fear, a desperate longing for the safety of his nest.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "f9e656cc-b8dc-ee92-bf11-7c18f90074a8"], "h5da3b8d1g37d4g46e9gb2f6g2edbbae947bc": ["*But his mother is gone - taken. All that's left are these <i>creatures</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "802232cb-c37f-4648-afc5-97199ebb0d4e"], "h0f32af83gc1c8g4281gbfb9ga34ebc0502ea": ["<i>Offer him your hand. He can follow your scent to your camp in the wilderness.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "10402276-5a5b-b905-e8fb-de2daa77a24c"], "h03cbc0ddg04a7g4705g9116g645631c30cb2": ["New home...? Maybe.", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "8a701006-69d0-95c3-6b91-48197dc5bb47"], "h7a2c94c0gdbf7g41f2gbb75gf4226a06c2e8": ["*He runs away. Only time will tell if he'll reappear.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "94be6338-7fee-2564-fdd7-923c3d471dcc"], "h4ce68d40g3959g4be3gb120g81fb3f1c3311": ["Got to get away from here first.", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "a1ba5ea3-8e4f-7991-9252-94ab78a54dea"], "hb337e84eg138ag4189gb74age8f6cb10576b": ["*The cub seems anxious to leave, but afraid to defy the goblins. They have to be dealt with, one way or the other.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "62009c89-dcfc-9661-5c36-5cec1fac0784"], "hb7b3e48bga8a9g4bc2g9cc2g0bcce08ae643": ["*The cub tilts his head. He's considering it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "f3bd5f13-69f5-ff6d-8978-ed8593070008"], "ha6d7b0bfga2ffg43a9gac5eg643d68683c6a": ["*Screech!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "9c77ede9-e604-4528-5803-b3282334e686"], "h723322bcge5aag4271g8267g9b02065deeaa": ["*Squawk!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "ed56084e-b2fb-7db8-fb34-6e760cca72c5"], "h24884f29g0e97g482dgb189ga576dbe1098d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "6b5ab48e-02cd-ea14-289d-e7b3e8d45e65"], "h80722415g4843g4502gaf0eg091961053a4e": ["*Hroo-hoot!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "309d5ad1-a0cc-c439-4cfd-2c229a8102a7"], "hbf38cc0agf92cg47acgbd6cgcb7a8fec21ac": ["*The cub breathes in shallow bursts, his chest heaving with the effort.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "28cceb03-fa8e-86df-ac6a-b3e2b859421c"], "hb764a75bg05c7g4dddg9d3dg5ddba90117b8": ["<i>Kneel - you won't hurt it.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "2d9ff558-b20a-3c60-7e07-6e6fd1eabb06"], "h965ce074gc569g4d9fgbef5g71e5fed33a3b": ["*Its talons bite deep into the earth, every muscle trembling. You realise it isn't afraid...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "b750a5c0-7299-97cb-4134-217aca2d9cc1"], "hb92db106gc424g4d60g86aeg7716a5b21b8c": ["*... it's <i>furious. </i>Rage blazes within it. Tear. Hunt. <i>Kill.*</i>", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "5790efbf-a7b1-b6d8-351f-cf3904bb9692"], "hb693ab66ga108g4e81g915bg7ce57f633f12": ["<i>Coax the cub toward the goalposts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "ba0893c9-6a58-b967-26c4-bdff43565ccf"], "h088b2ea7g38e3g4833ga86ag854271caf1d1": ["*The owlbear coos softly. He doesn't understand - but he trusts you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "4079d368-c3e2-d6ce-03cf-69b48c76a62e"], "h7a5c27e3gc1aeg452bgbd0fgc3d297a2713d": ["*The cub's feathers ruffle in distrust. With a defiant squawk, he bounds away.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "1ca11256-ae41-1bbf-457c-996fbaf0e798"], "h13bebbd4g6741g4a9bgbc83g345f1800a7e2": ["<i>Guide his gaze to the goblins - they deserve to die.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "34ccb571-8c09-12b6-2817-d46d164a7238"], "ha1fd27c7g23e9g4968gb2c9g5cc89a19df49": ["*The cub's beak snaps in the air, eager to rend<i>, yearning </i>for blood and soft belly-flesh.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "7642dacd-1a25-d96d-0266-fde25c777da2"], "hcb63a8d6g512eg4442gb300g3d12d2c786bc": ["*The cub clicks his beak weakly - more scared than afraid. He has no fight left in him.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "c15f6433-eab6-00a5-a398-bea919b0ed81"], "h7a4289e8g1122g47b7g9143gcc7eea0def1c": ["<i>Nod to the goalposts - he'll be safe there.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "1bc99212-8e05-67f3-57cc-96d50887f007"], "hcbf74d33g5848g44f2gb945g55feb4dea0f0": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "9e73c38f-8dfd-3162-8216-bd1958a2c4a9"], "h13bfc159g8efbg45b0ga5cdgbfd26dcdf88e": ["*Screech!*", "c66b2865-6613-4372-b97a-e330c1d75d09", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_ChickenChase_Owlbear.html", "58d942a6-4b53-ce36-476b-69c96c98f29a"]}